{"body":[{"content":"「字幕由 富睿字幕組 搬運」\n（禁止在B站宣傳漫遊相關内容，否則拉黑）","location":2,"from":0,"to":5},{"content":"老師…\n(3年級 春天 17歲)","from":7.215,"location":2,"to":8.258},{"content":"(3年級 春天 17歲)","from":8.258,"location":2,"to":8.967},{"content":"走廊上要靠右走\n(3年級 春天 17歲)","from":8.967,"location":2,"to":10.969},{"content":"請讓開","from":11.344,"location":2,"to":12.387},{"content":"還有…","from":13.555,"location":2,"to":14.305},{"content":"你盯著看學生的胸部看太久了","from":15.223,"location":2,"to":17.308},{"content":"謝謝","from":20.603,"location":2,"to":21.438},{"content":"會長只和那個老師關係不好呢","from":24.024,"location":2,"to":27.402},{"content":"發生過什麼事嗎","from":27.652,"location":2,"to":29.487},{"content":"我只是…","from":33.867,"location":2,"to":35.076},{"content":"討厭騙子而已","from":36.494,"location":2,"to":38.455},{"content":"(星期一的豐滿2 之二)","from":39.039,"location":2,"to":45.045},{"content":"老師…我喜歡你\n(1年級 冬天 15歲)","from":46.546,"location":2,"to":48.757},{"content":"(1年級 冬天 15歲)","from":48.757,"location":2,"to":49.299},{"content":"保密就好 請和我交往\n(1年級 冬天 15歲)","from":49.299,"location":2,"to":51.509},{"content":"為什麼…","from":57.098,"location":2,"to":58.058},{"content":"你看 可愛吧","from":64.314,"location":2,"to":65.982},{"content":"平常可看不到的喔","from":66.608,"location":2,"to":68.485},{"content":"為什麼","from":71.571,"location":2,"to":72.906},{"content":"老師的真心話","from":77.66,"location":2,"to":79.204},{"content":"我透過瀏海看得一清二楚喔","from":79.537,"location":2,"to":82.207},{"content":"我絕對會在畢業前讓你投降的","from":84.334,"location":2,"to":88.004},{"content":"(2年級 夏天 16歲)","from":98.389,"location":2,"to":101.559},{"content":"好厲害啊\n(2年級 夏天 16歲)","from":101.559,"location":2,"to":103.603},{"content":"才剛升上2年級就是王牌了呢","from":104.479,"location":2,"to":107.69},{"content":"成績也是年級頂尖","from":108.525,"location":2,"to":111.027},{"content":"而且最重要的是…","from":112.362,"location":2,"to":114.197},{"content":"好可愛","from":114.572,"location":2,"to":116.282},{"content":"學姊 再來一局","from":124.249,"location":2,"to":126.876},{"content":"(2年級 秋天 17歲)","from":131.172,"location":2,"to":131.881},{"content":"本次就任第80屆學生會會長…\n(2年級 秋天 17歲)","from":131.881,"location":2,"to":135.969},{"content":"她來擔任學生會會長的話","from":136.219,"location":2,"to":137.929},{"content":"學生會就能放心了呢","from":137.929,"location":2,"to":139.848},{"content":"哎呀 教務主任 當初入學的時候","from":140.184,"location":2,"to":143.18},{"content":"不是還因為瀏海的事把她叫過去嗎","from":143.184,"location":2,"to":146.312},{"content":"因為不是標準的髮型","from":147.105,"location":2,"to":149.357},{"content":"所以請她注意一下","from":149.357,"location":2,"to":151.151},{"content":"但被那瀏海後的視線盯著","from":151.484,"location":2,"to":154.154},{"content":"簡直就像被既有觀念束縛的自己","from":154.362,"location":2,"to":156.781},{"content":"被簾帷對面的貴族看透一般","from":156.99,"location":2,"to":161.202},{"content":"那也是她的特色呢","from":163.079,"location":2,"to":165.957},{"content":"只要以後不要被壞男人接近就好","from":167.083,"location":2,"to":170.962},{"content":"…請大家多多指教","from":170.962,"location":2,"to":172.172},{"content":"接著是新副會長的演說","from":173.173,"location":2,"to":176.176},{"content":"成績優秀 品行端正","from":178.428,"location":2,"to":181.347},{"content":"像她那樣的學生就是青春的理想型呢","from":181.764,"location":2,"to":185.435},{"content":"(3年級 夏天 18歲)","from":187.43,"location":2,"to":188.36},{"content":"我被他告白了\n(3年級 夏天 18歲)","from":188.36,"location":2,"to":191.94},{"content":"你覺得該怎麼辦呢","from":192.734,"location":2,"to":194.36},{"content":"老師 你想要怎麼做呢","from":205.914,"location":2,"to":208.166},{"content":"已經夠了…","from":214.923,"location":2,"to":215.798},{"content":"我要和他登上大人的階梯","from":216.966,"location":2,"to":220.136},{"content":"好好期待暑假結束的報告吧","from":227.936,"location":2,"to":231.105},{"content":"我馬上去拒絕","from":244.244,"location":2,"to":246.537},{"content":"(3年級 秋天 18歲)","from":249.165,"location":2,"to":251.459},{"content":"老師…\n(3年級 秋天 18歲)","from":251.459,"location":2,"to":252.377},{"content":"只有現在喔","from":252.919,"location":2,"to":254.295},{"content":"18歲學生 現任女子高中生的…","from":254.712,"location":2,"to":259.968},{"content":"H罩杯","from":261.886,"location":2,"to":263.429},{"content":"(畢業證書頒發典禮)","from":270.228,"location":2,"to":272.23},{"content":"到畢業前都沒能讓你認輸嗎","from":274.065,"location":2,"to":277.11},{"content":"是我輸了呢 老師","from":277.986,"location":2,"to":280.238},{"content":"所以…","from":282.615,"location":2,"to":283.533},{"content":"我今天也要從喜歡老師畢業了","from":284.158,"location":2,"to":286.995},{"content":"至今為止謝謝你了","from":291.165,"location":2,"to":293.167},{"content":"但是說謊要適可而止喔","from":294.711,"location":2,"to":297.422},{"content":"不然的話…","from":299.132,"location":2,"to":300.383},{"content":"會失去最重要的東西喔","from":302.593,"location":2,"to":305.054},{"content":"對不起…","from":326.034,"location":2,"to":326.868},{"content":"我果然沒辦法從喜歡老師畢業","from":328.036,"location":2,"to":331.831},{"content":"但是你看","from":335.752,"location":2,"to":336.836},{"content":"已經4月了喔","from":337.17,"location":2,"to":338.546},{"content":"這樣就和老師跟學生…","from":339.005,"location":2,"to":341.424},{"content":"沒有關係了吧","from":342.175,"location":2,"to":343.593},{"content":"這樣也還是不行嗎","from":345.72,"location":2,"to":347.555},{"content":"反正是愚人節","from":353.186,"location":2,"to":354.812},{"content":"謊話也可以","from":355.855,"location":2,"to":357.19},{"content":"就算是謊話也可以","from":358.524,"location":2,"to":359.984},{"content":"讓我聽聽老師真正的想法啊","from":360.234,"location":2,"to":364.572},{"content":"太好了","from":384.175,"location":2,"to":385.76},{"content":"錄到證言了","from":385.76,"location":2,"to":388.346},{"content":"順便一提","from":392.058,"location":2,"to":393.142},{"content":"這才是現在真正的時刻","from":393.142,"location":2,"to":396.521},{"content":"老師…","from":399.899,"location":2,"to":400.691},{"content":"這麼突然…","from":401.067,"location":2,"to":402.944},{"content":"等 等一下","from":402.944,"location":2,"to":404.404},{"content":"我還沒做好心理準備","from":404.404,"location":2,"to":406.948},{"content":"花瓣隨著春風飛舞飄落","from":411.244,"location":2,"to":416.707},{"content":"在熟悉的街道上奔馳而過","from":416.707,"location":2,"to":422.255},{"content":"本會是憂鬱的Monday","from":422.255,"location":2,"to":427.635},{"content":"但在你身旁邊就是Happy day","from":427.635,"location":2,"to":433.182},{"content":"雖有些難以言喻","from":433.182,"location":2,"to":438.688},{"content":"但滿溢的心情卻無法止息","from":438.688,"location":2,"to":443.734},{"content":"你能聽見我胸口激情的心跳嗎","from":443.734,"location":2,"to":449.615},{"content":"亦近(亦遠)的心與心","from":449.615,"location":2,"to":455.371},{"content":"愛的形式有無限多","from":455.371,"location":2,"to":460.543},{"content":"但豐滿的思念永遠只有一個","from":460.543,"location":2,"to":466.299}]}